1.00	Gavin_Packard	Gavin Packard	Gavin Packard is a British origin Indian actor. He had worked in Bollywood as well as other Indian language films like Malayalam, Telugu etc. He played the villain roles in many super hit films of 90's like Mohra, Tadipaar and Chamatkar. He had also acted in Malayalam films like Aayushkalam, Season, Aanaval Mothiram, Aryan. However, he left Indian industry at the early millennium. He was noted for his cruel villain role and he was some of very few foreign actors in Indian film industry.	
